      "Audit reports are sensitive: senior security admins receive full detail (responsible for remediation); senior management receives high-level summary (demonstrates due care); distribute on need-to-know basis",
      "User entitlement audits verify least privilege is enforced; focus especially on privileged accounts; cloud platforms offer scheduled access reviews; users can self-request access removal",
      "Security oversight activities: log reviews (admin/privileged actions), account management reviews (authorised users only), backup verification, KPI/risk indicator reviews, internal and external audits",
      "Additional pentesting techniques: War dialing = dialling phone numbers to find modems/PBX systems (legacy but still tested); Sniffing = passively capturing network traffic (requires network access or wireless proximity); Dumpster diving = searching discarded materials for sensitive info (physical security gap); War driving = driving to find open/vulnerable Wi-Fi networks",
