      "Vulnerability management lifecycle: Discover (asset inventory + authenticated scans) → Prioritise (CVSS + business context + exploitability) → Assess (validate findings, remove false positives) → Report (communicate to asset owners with SLA deadlines) → Remediate (patch, mitigate, or formally accept with documented rationale) → Verify (re-scan to confirm closure); typical SLAs: Critical = 24–72 hr, High = 7 days, Medium = 30 days, Low = 90 days",
