      "CIS Benchmarks and DISA STIGs: CIS Benchmarks = community-developed configuration guides for OS, applications, and cloud; Level 1 = basic, low-impact recommendations for all environments; Level 2 = advanced, higher security at cost of some functionality — for high-security environments; DISA STIGs (Security Technical Implementation Guides) = US DoD mandatory hardening standards; SCAP (Security Content Automation Protocol) enables automated compliance checking using XCCDF and OVAL content against STIGs and CIS Benchmarks",
